      "id": "stalemate-safety",
      "title": "Winning Still Needs Care",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "id": "b02-c07-p01",
          "type": "prose",
          "body_md": "Stalemate happens when the side to move has no legal move but is not in check. Beginners often stalemate with a queen because they take every escape square without giving check."
